## ⚡ Pour modifier le statut global

```python
def set_global_status(conn, product, action, region, environment, new_status, user):
    with conn.cursor() as cur:
        cur.execute("""
            INSERT INTO ecosystem_access (product_name, action_name, region, environment, global_status, ecosystem_overrides, updated_by)
            VALUES (%s, %s, %s, %s, %s, '{}', %s)
            ON CONFLICT (product_name, action_name, region, environment)
            DO UPDATE SET global_status = EXCLUDED.global_status,
                          updated_at = now(),
                          updated_by = EXCLUDED.updated_by;
        """, (product, action, region, environment, new_status, user))
    conn.commit()
```

